text: KUMP-LP (107.9 FM) is a low-power radio station broadcasting a religious format as an affiliate of Radio 74 Internationale. Licensed to Days Creek, Oregon, United States, the station is currently owned by Umpqua Christian Radio. ==References== ==External links== * UMP-LP UMP-LP Category:Religious radio stations in the United States Category:Douglas County, Oregon UMP-LP
